or abuse variadic args:
`func CopyFromArchive(ctx context.Context, nameOrID string, path string, reader io.Reader, options ...*CopyOptions) (entities.ContainerCopyFunc, error)`  making the option argument optional
just kidding :laughing: 
I'll do as you proposed.

More sane alternative might be `options pattern` (although it's not used in rest of the API which would be little bit inconsistent):

```diff
diff --git a/pkg/bindings/containers/archive.go b/pkg/bindings/containers/archive.go
